Description

Delight in the delicate, nutty flavor of butternut squash ravioli, complemented by fragrant sage, enveloped in a rich brown butter sauce.

Ingredients

  • Butternut Squash: 2 cups, cubed
  • Ravioli Dough: 1 batch
  • Parmesan Cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • Fresh Sage: 10 leaves
  • Unsalted Butter: 1/2 cup
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Nutmeg: 1/4 teaspoon
  • Egg: 1, beaten (for sealing ravioli)
